io.smudgr.engine.alg.select

Class Selector

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.smudgr.engine.param.Parametric
      • io.smudgr.engine.SmudgeComponent
        • io.smudgr.engine.alg.AlgorithmComponent
          • io.smudgr.engine.alg.select.Selector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProjectItem, ReflectableType
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AllSelect, EdgeSelect, RangeSelect

    public abstract class Selector
extends AlgorithmComponent
    The abstract Selector class defines an AlgorithmComponent that uses actual pixel values of an image to focus an Operation. A CoordFunction generates a pixel order but Selector implementations narrow that set down based on pixel value.
